title: Becoming the Swordmaster Rank Young Lord of the Sichuan Tang Family
description: Becoming the Swordmaster Rank Young Lord of the Sichuan Tang Family Becoming the Sacheon Dang’s Swordsmaster-Rank Young Lord , Becoming the Sacheon Tang’s Sword God Level Young Lord , 사천당가의 검신급 소가주가 되었다 , Он стал главой семьи Четырех Небесных Дангов , He Became the Swordmaster , Rank Young Lord of the Tang Family of Sacheon , He Became the Head of the Four Heavenly Dang Family Once a prestigious lineage of poison and hidden weapons, the Sichuan Tang Family has now fallen into decline. Born there, Tang Yeon-myeong suddenly becomes obsessed with sword, awakening memories of his past life where he reached the pinnacle of swordsmanship. “In this life, I want to live quietly.” To live quietly, I must hide my swordsmanship skills. However, there are too many obstacles hindering me.
